Here is the cleaned up text:

Export Your Capacity Plan

Export your capacity plan as a CSV file.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions


USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To view, create, edit, and delete workload histories, intelligent forecasts, and capacity plans:	Workforce Engagement Analyst

Open Capacity Plans in the App Launcher.
Click to open a capacity plan.
Click Export.
Click Export to confirm.
The CSV file downloads to your default downloads folder.
title: Service Cloud Capacity Planning
